           MOVE SUB-T-C-IVA TO SUB-T-C-IVA1.
           MOVE SUC-C-IVA TO SUC-C-IVA1.
           MOVE COM-IVA TO COM-IVA1.
           MOVE NETO-IVA TO NETO-IVA1.
           MOVE NO-GRA-IVA TO NO-GRA-IVA1.
           MOVE EXE-IVA TO EXE-IVA1.
           MOVE DED-IVA TO DED-IVA1.
           MOVE RET-IVA TO RET-IVA1.
           MOVE IMP-1-IVA TO IMP-1-IVA1.
           MOVE IMP-2-IVA TO IMP-2-IVA1.
           MOVE CRE-DEB-IVA TO CRE-DEB-IVA1.
           MOVE PER-IVA TO PER-IVA1.
           MOVE ALI-IVA TO ALI-IVA1.
           MOVE DIA-VAL-IVA TO DIA-VAL-IVA1.
           MOVE MES-VAL-IVA TO MES-VAL-IVA1.
           MOVE ANO-VAL-IVA TO ANO-VAL-IVA1.
